The Kardashians Users will have access to features like high-quality viewing, up to four concurrent streams, 4k video quality for select titles and the ability to set up to seven different profiles, including the ability for parents to set kids’ profiles to access age-appropriate content. The Walt Disney Company has announced that South Africans can now register early to subscribe to its Disney+ streaming service, with the company offering an exclusive introductory offer of R950. Read: Netflix losing customers for the first time in a decade – will introduce a cheaper, advertising-supported option